50|$|You are dealt a hand of six cards. If {{you have}} no {{characters}} in your initial hand, you return your hand to the <b>draw</b> <b>pile</b> and <b>draw</b> a fresh hand, continuing to do so until you {{have at least one}} character in your hand.|$|R
