25|$|Note {{that play}} {{continues}} after the <b>draw</b> <b>pile</b> is exhausted, each player playing or discarding one card per turn. Once both players {{run out of}} cards in their hand with a depleted <b>draw</b> <b>pile,</b> play ends.|$|R
